  "title": "Sales Engineer (B2B, Automotive Battery, Class 3)",
  "description": "<ul><li>Overall responsible for providing energy solutions to our corporate customers through promoting a wide range of industrial batteries.</li><li>Generate sales to achieve profitability and distribution objectives, performing sales administration duties, troubleshooting technical issues and liaising with logistics team for goods delivery.</li></ul><p>Requirements:</p><ul><li>Diploma and above</li><li>At least 2 years of experience in <strong>industrial sales/battery product sales</strong>.</li><li>Possess own vehicle.</li></ul><p>If you are keen to apply for the position, kindly email your detailed resume in<strong> MS Word </strong>to<strong> hr@recruit-expert.com</strong></p><p>Please note that only shortlisted candidates will be notified.</p><p>For more job opportunities, please visit our website at<strong> </strong><a href=\"http://www.recruit-expert.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><strong>www.recruit-expert.com</strong></a></p><p>EA Licence: 19C9701</p><p>Registration: R21100996</p>",
